Yassin &amp; David, sp. n. d, 
<taxonomicName id="C134E081664403D4DECCE362261A3159" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Zaprionus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zaprionus lachaisei" order="Diptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lachaisei">Zaprionus lachaisei</taxonomicName>
Yassin &amp; David, sp. n. e and 
<taxonomicName id="233A8CC23A113F1FF1B51E43C5F7D444" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Zaprionus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zaprionus vittiger" order="Diptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="47" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vittiger">Zaprionus vittiger</taxonomicName>
Coquillett, 1902 f.
</paragraph>
